quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,190,Ngempela ekudalweni kwamazulu nomhlaba nokuguquguquka kobusuku nemini ngempela kuyizimpawu kulabo abaqondayo
  3,191,"Labo abakhumbula uMvelinqangi bemile noma behleli noma (belele) ngezinhlangothi zabo futhi becabanga ngokudalwa kwamazulu nomhlaba (bethi), “Nkosi yethu awukudalanga lokhu ngokungenhloso udumo malube kuwena ngakho-ke sivikele esijezisweni somlilo"
  3,192,Nkosi yethu! Ngempela noma ngabe ubani omfaka emlilweni umhlazile futhi izoni angeke zibe nabo abasizi
  3,193,"Nkosi yethu ngempela thina simzwile ummemezi ememela enkolweni (ethi) kholwani enkosini yenu, ngakho-ke sabe sesiyakholwa, Nkosi yethu sithethelele izono zethu nokuthi ucishe izenzo zethu ezimbi futhi senze ukuba sife kanye nabalungileyo"
  3,194,Nkosi yethu! Futhi siphe lokho owasethembisa kona esithunyweni sakho futhi ungasihlazi ngosuku lokuvuka kwabafileyo ngempela wena awusephuli isithembiso (sakho)”
  3,195,"Ngakho-ke iNkosi yabo yabaphendula (emithandazweni yabo). Angisoze ngavumela ukuba kulahleke umsebenzi wanoma ngabe yisiphi isisebenzi phakathi kwenu, noma ngabe isilisa noma ngabe isifazane abanye benu bayingxenye yabanye, ngakho-ke labo abafuduka futhi abakhishwa emakhaya abo futhi behlushwa endleleni yami, balwa futhi babulawa ngempela ngiyosula izenzo zabo ezimbi bese ngibafaka ezivandeni okugobhoza imifula ngaphansi kwazo (lokho) kungumvuzo ovela kuMvelinqangi futhi kuMvelinqangi kunemivuzo engcono kakhulu"
  3,196,Nize ningakhohliswa ukuyaluza kwalabo abangakholwa ezweni
  3,197,Kuyinjabulo encane ngakho-ke indawo yabo yokuhlala kuyoba isihogo futhi yimbi (leyo) ndawo yokuphumula
  3,198,"Kodwa labo abesaba iNkosi yabo okwabo yizivande okugobhoza imifula ngaphansi kwazo, bayohlala khona ingunaphakade lokho kuyinjabulo evela kuMvelinqangi futhi lokho okukuMvelinqangi kungcono kakhulu kulabo abalungile"
  3,199,"Futhi ngempela phakathi kwabantu bencwadi kukhona labo abakholwa kuMvelinqangi nakulokho okwembulwa kunina nakulokho okwembulwa kubona, bezithoba ngokuzinikela kuMvelinqangi abawathengi amavesi kaMvelinqangi ngenani elincane labo-ke okwabo umvuzo wabo useNkosini yabo ngempela uMvelinqangi ungosheshayo ekubaleni (ekwahluleleni)"
  3,200,Oh nina enikholwayo! Bekezelani ngisho nangaphezulu kokubezela futhi nibe munye nesabe uMvelinqangi ukuze niphumelele